@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<section class="page-header">
    <span class="section-kicker">About</span>
    <h1>Getting To Know Me</h1>
    <p>
        I am a second-year student with a growing interest in technology, especially web
        development, interface design, and building projects that solve everyday student needs.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="content-grid">
    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Academic Focus</h2>
        <p>
            I am currently strengthening my foundation in programming logic, database concepts, and software
            development workflows through hands-on coursework and guided practice projects.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Goals</h2>
        <p>
            My goal is to become a confident developer who can create clean, responsive, and useful applications
            while continuing to improve my communication, teamwork, and technical problem-solving skills.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Interests</h2>
        <p>
            I enjoy learning new tools, designing simple but modern interfaces, and exploring how technology
            can make class projects more engaging and effective.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Student Mindset</h2>
        <p>
            I see myself as curious, adaptable, and motivated, and I believe that consistent practice and
            experimentation are the best ways for me to grow in tech at this stage of my journey.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
